## Diameter Author/Authen Statemachine

Simple implementation of state machine that represents the authorisation/authentication states for a Diameter session.

## Details

The <a class="ahl-group-only" data-ids="0cefce8ca6962a44">state machine definition</a> group defines the following flow chart diagram using the flow2uml node package.

The same group then also defines the code for the <a class="ahl-node-only" data-ids="54e349a080dc8137">diameter_statem_authorisation_two</a> module that contains the workings the statemachine that is defined using this <a class="ahl-node-only" data-ids="7adc197f63c113b1">[diameter_statem_authorisation_two]	‚ûù</a> node.


